# DevExpress Spreadsheet (tùy chọn)

**NuGet:** Package DevExpress .NET phải dùng feed công ty. Xem rule **bcdt-devexpress-nuget** và `nuget.config` (feed: https://devexpress.aequitas.dev/nuget).

## Backend - Generate Workbook (C#)
```csharp
using DevExpress.Spreadsheet;

// ✅ Create workbook
using var workbook = new Workbook();
var sheet = workbook.Worksheets[0];

// ✅ Set values and formatting
sheet.Cells["A1"].Value = "Header";
sheet.Cells["A1"].Font.Bold = true;
sheet.Cells["A1"].Fill.BackgroundColor = Color.LightGray;

// ✅ Lock/unlock cells
sheet.Protect("", SheetProtectionOptions.Default);
sheet.Range["B2:B100"].Protection.Locked = false; // Editable cells
```

## Backend - Save to Hybrid Storage
```csharp
// 1. Save JSON (Layer 1 - full state)
submission.Presentation.WorkbookJson = workbook.SaveToJson();

// 2. Extract to relational (Layer 2 - for queries)
foreach (var row in editableRows)
{
    var dataRow = new ReportDataRow { ... };
    // Map cells to NumericValue1, TextValue1, etc.
}

// 3. Calculate summary (Layer 2.5)
submission.Summary.TotalValue1 = dataRows.Sum(r => r.NumericValue1);
```

## Frontend - Spreadsheet Component (React)
```tsx
import { Spreadsheet } from 'devextreme-react/spreadsheet';

const ExcelEditor: React.FC<{ workbookJson: string }> = ({ workbookJson }) => {
  const spreadsheetRef = useRef<Spreadsheet>(null);
  
  const handleSave = async () => {
    const json = spreadsheetRef.current?.instance.getDocument();
    await submissionApi.save({ workbookJson: json });
  };

  return (
    <Spreadsheet
      ref={spreadsheetRef}
      height={600}
      documentFormat="json"
      documentSource={workbookJson}
    />
  );
};
```

## Data Binding Flow
1. Load FormDefinition with DataBindings
2. Resolve each binding (DB, API, Reference, Formula)
3. Populate cells with resolved values
4. Lock non-editable cells
5. Return JSON to frontend
